1-Welcome Screen
Welcome to Banking System
(choose an option)
    a-Create an Account
    b-Show Balance
    c-Deposit Money
    d-Withdraw Money
    e-Close Bank Account (DELETE)

A- Creation of Account
Name            varchar notnull

B- Show Account
input <- AccountNumber
output -> Balance

C- Deposit Money
input <- Account Number, Ammount
output -> Confirmation Message

D- Withdraw Money
input <- AccountNumber, Ammount
output -> Confirmation Message

E- Close Account
input <- AccountNumber
output -> Confirmation Message



Bank Account :-
Name    Account number  Bank balance
Aryan   100             1500

Activity:-
Account number  Action  Amount
100             Debit   300

